<br>
Plane of Fear can be done with a single group, as can the Plane of Hate. You have to draw the line somewhere. Basically, the meeting decided the line would be drawn between efreeti and fire giants.  Respawn time is also an issue, but I think the fact that younger raiders need something to cut their teeth on is important.  Also, if you are strong enough to do fire giants with a single group, what the hell are you doing raiding them? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Even if you do need something from FGs, what's the problem with scheduling it like everyone else?</font><P><HR align="center" size="2" width="33%">
